{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775884476193,"sessionID":"ses_2850a6bffffeycy4lHOS3Q6Or6","part":{"id":"prt_d7af69ec7001AmTjfb15zfljUF","messageID":"msg_d7af677ee001kp7rxbOAd2hqYA","sessionID":"ses_2850a6bffffeycy4lHOS3Q6Or6","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-240af649ed804d8286300c0a3a814cb1","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/testing/agentcube_tdd_manifest.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/testing/agentcube_tdd_manifest.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AgentCube 核心模块测试契约 (TDD Manifest)\n2: \n3: 本规范定义了系统各核心组件必须实现的最小测试集。未通过以下测试用例的实现将被判定为“跑偏”。\n4: \n5: ## 1. Workload Manager (Go) - 核心准入测试\n6: - **Func: `CreateSandbox`**\n7:     - **Test-WM-1**: 必须 Mock Kubernetes Client，验证 `sandbox` 资源被正确创建。\n8:     - **Test-WM-2**: 验证 Session 冲突处理（同名 Sandbox 冲突时返回 409 或恢复现有会话）。\n9:     - **Test-WM-3**: 验证 Pod 状态同步逻辑。模拟 Pod 变为 `Running` 状态，验证 API 返回正确的 `Endpoint`。\n10: - **Func: `DeleteSession`**\n11:     - **Test-WM-4**: 验证物理资源的清理。确保调用了 K8s Delete API 且 Redis 记录同步删除。\n12: \n13: ## 2. Router (Go) - 高并发与安全测试\n14: - **Middleware: `AuthMiddleware`**\n15:     - **Test-RT-1**: 构造非法 JWT，验证返回 `401 Unauthorized`。\n16:     - **Test-RT-2**: 构造过期 JWT，验证返回 `Token Expired`。\n17: - **Proxy Logic: `HandleProxy`**\n18:     - **Test-RT-3**: 模拟后端超时，验证 Proxy 正确处理 `Gateway Timeout` 且不崩溃。\n19:     - **Test-RT-4**: 验证 Header 透传（Host, X-Forwarded-For 等）。\n20: \n21: ## 3. Session Store (Go) - 强一致性测试\n22: - **Store Interface: `RedisStore` / `ValkeyStore`**\n23:     - **Test-ST-1**: 验证对象序列化与反序列化（SessionInfo -> JSON -> SessionInfo）。\n24:     - **Test-ST-2**: 并发写测试。模拟 100 个并发请求写入同一 Session，验证无 Data Race。\n25: \n26: ## 4. PicoD (Go) - 执行引擎隔离测试\n27: - **Executor: `RunCode`**\n28:     - **Test-PD-1**: 验证资源限制（如 OOM）。模拟大内存分配，验证进程被正确杀掉并返回错误。\n29:     - **Test-PD-2**: 验证 Stdout 分块读取。处理超过 1MB 的输出，验证无缓冲区溢出。\n30: \n31: ## 5. Python SDK & CLI - 兼容性与易用性测试\n32: - **Class: `CodeInterpreterClient`**\n33:     - **Test-SDK-1**: 验证所有 HTTP 状态码映射。404 -> `NotFoundError`, 429 -> `RateLimitError`。\n34:     - **Test-SDK-2**: 验证文件上传协议。构造二进制流，验证 Multipart 封装符合 Router 规范。\n35: - **CLI: `kubectl-agentcube`**\n36:     - **Test-CLI-1**: 验证 `run` 命令的参数解析。测试 `--image`, `--env` 等参数的正确合并。\n37: \n38: ## 物理指标要求\n39: 1.  **测试/代码行数比 (T/C Ratio)**: 必须 > 0.4 (即每 100 行代码至少 40 行测试)。\n40: 2.  **用例完整性**: 每个源文件（`*.go`, `*.py`）必须存在对应的 `*_test.go` 或 `test_*.py`。\n\n(End of file - total 40 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AgentCube 核心模块测试契约 (TDD Manifest)\n\n本规范定义了系统各核心组件必须实现的最小测试集。未通过以下测试用例的实现将被判定为“跑偏”。\n\n## 1. Workload Manager (Go) - 核心准入测试\n- **Func: `CreateSandbox`**\n    - **Test-WM-1**: 必须 Mock Kubernetes Client，验证 `sandbox` 资源被正确创建。\n    - **Test-WM-2**: 验证 Session 冲突处理（同名 Sandbox 冲突时返回 409 或恢复现有会话）。\n    - **Test-WM-3**: 验证 Pod 状态同步逻辑。模拟 Pod 变为 `Running` 状态，验证 API 返回正确的 `Endpoint`。\n- **Func: `DeleteSession`**\n    - **Test-WM-4**: 验证物理资源的清理。确保调用了 K8s Delete API 且 Redis 记录同步删除。\n\n## 2. Router (Go) - 高并发与安全测试\n- **Middleware: `AuthMiddleware`**\n    - **Test-RT-1**: 构造非法 JWT，验证返回 `401 Unauthorized`。\n    - **Test-RT-2**: 构造过期 JWT，验证返回 `Token Expired`。\n- **Proxy Logic: `HandleProxy`**\n    - **Test-RT-3**: 模拟后端超时，验证 Proxy 正确处理 `Gateway Timeout` 且不崩溃。\n    - **Test-RT-4**: 验证 Header 透传（Host, X-Forwarded-For 等）。\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/testing/agentcube_tdd_manifest.md","time":{"start":1775884476179,"end":1775884476192}}}}
